    <p>One of the most common questions we get from new Drupal users is, "Which modules do people normally use?"</p>
<p>That's a big question, with over 20,000 modules, but some are far more popular than others.</p>
<p>Webchick, one of the Drupal core developers, has used the statistics available on Drupal.org to <a href="http://gist.github.com/webchickenator/956a2d7a49c7490fefb5#file-gistfile1-txt-L14-L64">make a list of the most popular Drupal 7 modules</a>. This is different from the public stats on Drupal.org module pages which show the popularity of modules across all versions.</p>
